-- Tier A: full party/signature professionalization for 25 bilateral
-- agreement generators (NDA, contracts, leases, employment, etc). This
-- REPLACES the entire fields_schema for each slug with a restructured
-- schema using the party/signature field types (same engine already
-- powering the Rental Agreement and Quotation generators). Safe to run
-- more than once: each statement sets fields_schema to its final target
-- state, so re-running is a no-op once applied.

